 This Bill is very important for the socio economic 

and educational development of the nation.  India is emerging as a leading country 

in  the  field  of  information  and  technology.    Since  1990s  India  has  been 

continuously  marching  ahead  in  software  and  other  sectors.    After  Allahabad, 

Gwalior,  Jabalpur  and  Kanchipuram,  fifth  institute  is  being  started  in  Andhra 

Pradesh. 

 

